        "tactics": [
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "tactic",
                "name": "During Combat",
                "text": "The barbarian charges into the heart of battle, using one end of his double axe two-handed when charging or moving, and switching back to a double weapon grip when making full attacks. He uses his leaping and Acrobatics to enter melee quickly, using his no escape ability to chase down cowards."
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "tactic",
                "name": "Base Statistics",
                "text": "When not raging, the barbarian\u2019s statistics are <b>AC </b>19, touch 14, flat-footed 15; <b>hp </b>109; <b>Fort </b>+11, <b>Will </b>+6; no bonus vs. spells and spell-like or supernatural abilities; <b>DR </b>2/\u2014; <b>Melee</b><i>+1 orc double axe </i>+16/+11/+6 (1d8+5/19\u201320/\u00d73) or <i>+1 orc double axe </i>+14/+9/+4 (1d8+4/19\u201320/\u00d73), <i>+1 orc double axe </i>+14/+9 (1d8+4/19\u201320/\u00d73), bite +9 (1d4+1); <b>Ranged </b>mwk composite longbow +16/+11/+6 (1d8+3/\u00d73); <b>Str </b>16, <b>Con </b>14; <b>CMB </b>+14; <b>CMD </b>28; <b>Skills </b>Acrobatics +17 (+21 when jumping) Climb +8, Swim +8."
